LeBron James for help

35:58.590 --> 36:00.659
instead of you
simple snowflakes,

36:00.792 --> 36:03.862
who I feed, clothe
and pay six figures a year.

36:03.995 --> 36:05.864
Or get a free
top-tier education.

36:05.997 --> 36:08.133
