Goddamn it.

36:30.121 --> 36:31.890
[softly] Goddamn.

36:34.960 --> 36:36.762
Come on, fellas.
Eat up.

36:37.496 --> 36:39.030
[LeMarcus scoffs]

36:39.164 --> 36:42.000
Y'all can hate me
all you want.

36:42.133 --> 36:44.470
