y'all should be hatin'.

36:44.603 --> 36:47.673
Ain't me cashing out
on millions of dollars
a year

36:47.806 --> 36:50.676
while y'all can't pay rent,
can't put gas in y'all whips.

36:50.809 --> 36:52.844
If you even have a whip.
[scoffs]

36:52.978 --> 36:55.046
For 55 years,

36:55.180 --> 36:58.417
guys like you ate, drank,
fucked and played ball.

36:58.550 --> 37:00.686
We're just happy with
a free education, right?

37:00.819 --> 37:03.088
Nice free suit?
That shit'll keep us
happy, right?

37:03.221 --> 37:05.391
They know how to get us.
But not no more, okay?

37:05.524 --> 37:07.726
This shit is capitalism
at its finest.

37:07.859 --> 37:09.428
Greed at its worst.

37:09.561 --> 37:12.764
Everybody around us
got private jets
and private chefs,

37:12.898 --> 37:15.501
and we can't even
accept a fucking
free meal as a gift.

37:15.634 --> 37:17.736
Yeah. Yeah, that's right.
That pizza slice
right there,

37:17.869 --> 37:19.571
double fistin'
with them shits,

37:19.705 --> 37:22.073
that kid kicked out
of college twice. Shit.

37:22.207 --> 37:25.444
And we out there
every single day.
Blood, sweat and tears.

37:25.577 --> 37:27.045
You remember
your ankle, bro? Hmm?

37:27.178 --> 37:28.947
Remember when it swole up
like a watermelon?

37:29.080 --> 37:31.750
