gonna make you feel
in 30 years.

37:34.286 --> 37:36.322
You ain't got no medical.
You got insurance?

37:36.455 --> 37:38.824
What you gonna fix
your broken body with, huh?
Duct tape?

37:38.957 --> 37:40.959
Gorilla Glue the shits
back together?
What we gonna do?

37:41.092 --> 37:42.761
That's how y'all got to be
thinking about this.

37:42.894 --> 37:44.430
Where do we want to be
in 30 years from now?

37:44.563 --> 37:47.198
It starts right now.
It starts right here.

37:51.737 --> 37:53.104
Who bought
all this Pizza Hut?

37:57.242 --> 37:59.177
[LeMarcus] Look,
I'll be the first to say it.

37:59.311 --> 38:01.747
Lazor's taught me a lot
about more than just football.

38:01.880 --> 38:04.650
But what I began to realize
is I was being brainwashed,

38:04.783 --> 38:06.652
just like all of y'all.

38:06.785 --> 38:09.621
Scared of speaking up
because it was easy
to go along to get along.

38:09.755 --> 38:11.823
Don't let them tell you
there ain't enough
to go around.

38:11.957 --> 38:14.493
They got so much money,
they don't even know
where to put the shits.

38:14.626 --> 38:16.094
Y'all okay with that?

38:16.227 --> 38:18.229
All right.
You okay with that?

38:18.364 --> 38:21.299
[person] Guys, don't think
this isn't a two-way street.

38:21.433 --> 38:23.335
Where do you green fucks

38:23.469 --> 38:27.272
think you're transferring to
if I bury your ass
on the pine?

38:27.406 --> 38:29.941
I own your future.

38:30.075 --> 38:33.612
Where the hell
is LeMarcus?

38:33.745 --> 38:35.681
Let's be real.

38:35.814 --> 38:38.149
There are 12,500
draft-eligible players

38:38.283 --> 38:40.552
for the NFL
every single year,

38:40.686 --> 38:42.588
and only 300 of us
get drafted.

38:42.721 --> 38:44.990
That means
over 12,000 of us

38:45.123 --> 38:47.359
participate
in a multi-billion-
dollar industry

38:47.493 --> 38:48.994
that won't even give us
health insurance.

38:49.127 --> 38:51.630
