And they make you work it

39:00.038 --> 39:02.641
like it's a full-time job,
don't they? That's right.

39:02.774 --> 39:05.544
What about all those bullshit
classes they make you take
to stay on the field, huh?

39:05.677 --> 39:07.846
Hey, you remember
the Swahili shit
y'all was taking?

39:07.979 --> 39:11.049
