Seriously?

39:30.235 --> 39:31.537
Bank it.

39:33.405 --> 39:36.074
And even if it means
the death of me,
y'all can say,

39:36.207 --> 39:40.245
"I got caught up
with that crazy motherfucker
and his dreams of glory.

39:40.378 --> 39:42.380
And if I can do it,
then we can do it,

39:42.514 --> 39:45.383
and we could set ourselves up
and future generations
to come.

39:45.517 --> 39:47.318
Tell 'em about the barn, LJ.

39:47.453 --> 39:49.921
'Cause there
is a barn in Galilee
with grain filled so high

39:50.055 --> 39:51.557
that they won't even
sell it all.

39:51.690 --> 39:54.159
And you know what God says?
He says, "You poor fools.

39:54.292 --> 39:57.362
You may think that you're rich,
but you are poor
in the eyes of God."

39:57.496 --> 40:00.966
Why? Because
my people are hungry,
and your barn is full.

40:01.099 --> 40:03.735
-Make it plain!
-There is a barn in Galilee

40:03.869 --> 40:06.204
filled with grain,
and we out here starving.

40:06.337 --> 40:08.073
God is with us.

40:08.206 --> 40:11.577
He says
there is nothing to lose.
There is nothing to fear.

40:11.710 --> 40:15.547
I am here, and there is
nothing to fear!

40:18.684 --> 40:20.285
[panting]

40:25.056 --> 40:27.358
[upbeat country music playing]

40:34.299 --> 40:36.067
