[chuckles]

40:36.902 --> 40:38.236
Boo.

40:38.369 --> 40:40.472
[both chuckle]

40:40.606 --> 40:43.008
[upbeat country music
continues playing]

40:47.613 --> 40:49.080
Come with me.

40:49.214 --> 40:50.949
[chuckling]

40:51.082 --> 40:53.118
I plan to, baby.

40:55.353 --> 40:57.155
I mean it.

40:58.524 --> 40:59.991
Start a new chapter.

41:03.428 --> 41:05.631
You really
want me there?

41:07.398 --> 41:08.466
I do.

41:10.168 --> 41:11.503
[softly] Really?

41:44.603 --> 41:46.672
[all howl]

41:46.805 --> 41:48.574
[cheering]

41:48.707 --> 41:50.842
[announcer] Give it up
for French Montana!

41:50.976 --> 41:52.343
[hip-hop music playing]

41:52.477 --> 41:55.146
You like that?
You like that, baby?

41:55.280 --> 41:56.481
That was for y'all.

41:57.448 --> 42:00.652
[howls]

42:00.786 --> 42:02.854
Keep 'em coming.
You got it.

42:02.988 --> 42:05.190
Hey, what's your hurry?

42:06.692 --> 42:09.160
Rodger.
Brett.

42:09.294 --> 42:12.163
I've been head of
the booster club since '98.

42:12.297 --> 42:15.066
