a national title game

42:15.200 --> 42:17.435
in your own luxury box,
Brett?

42:17.569 --> 42:18.937
No.

42:19.070 --> 42:23.041
Lobster, filet mignon,
blow.

42:23.174 --> 42:25.343
Whatever
your heart desires.

42:25.476 --> 42:26.745
It sounds awesome.

42:26.878 --> 42:30.515
You wanna come with?
I can get you a ticket.

42:30.649 --> 42:32.718
