42:32.851 --> 42:37.055
Oh, they'll play.
Don't you worry your pretty
little head about that.

42:37.188 --> 42:40.959
Gonna find me
my quarterback,
and it'll be Easy Street.

42:43.261 --> 42:45.030
Five hundred dollars.

42:45.163 --> 42:47.098
