get me, Brett?

42:47.232 --> 42:49.234
A room number.

42:49.367 --> 42:51.136
What time
do you get off?

42:51.269 --> 42:53.271
[chuckles] Not mine.

42:56.407 --> 42:58.076
[knocking]

42:59.310 --> 43:01.579
[person]
LeMarcus. Emmett.

43:01.713 --> 43:02.848
[knocking]

43:02.981 --> 43:04.916
It's Rodger and Taylor.
Open up.

43:05.050 --> 43:06.918
[knocking continues]
[sighs]

43:07.052 --> 43:08.987
