43:38.383 --> 43:40.585
Yes. We're owed.

43:40.719 --> 43:44.522
Taylor.
What I think my associate
is trying to communicate here

43:44.656 --> 43:45.991
is that we're hurtin'.

43:46.124 --> 43:49.160
