1:04:52.957 --> 1:04:54.758
Splash it
all over Twitter too.

1:04:55.993 --> 1:04:58.228
I am joined now
by LeMarcus James,

1:04:58.362 --> 1:05:00.264
who won this year's
Heisman Trophy

1:05:00.397 --> 1:05:04.068
and has now rocked
the entire world of sports
and well beyond

1:05:04.201 --> 1:05:06.603
with his boycott
of the national title game,

1:05:06.736 --> 1:05:08.939
which is scheduled
for tomorrow
in New Orleans.

1:05:09.073 --> 1:05:11.675
LeMarcus, I'm gonna jump
right into the question
everyone is asking.

1:05:11.808 --> 1:05:15.379
Are you boycotting this game
and demanding compensation

1:05:15.512 --> 1:05:17.781
because of an unfortunate
medical condition

1:05:17.914 --> 1:05:20.584
that could jeopardize
your status in the draft?

1:05:20.717 --> 1:05:22.086
Good morning, Greeny.

1:05:22.219 --> 1:05:24.721
The answer is no.
