1:05:30.894 --> 1:05:32.729
But name me an NFL team
that wouldn't take

1:05:32.862 --> 1:05:34.764
eight to 20 years
of elite quarterback play.

1:05:34.898 --> 1:05:37.501
You see, the reality is,
this isn't about me.

1:05:37.634 --> 1:05:39.303
This is about
our current system.

1:05:39.436 --> 1:05:41.938
It's about my fellow
D-I athletes and teammates

1:05:42.072 --> 1:05:43.473
who have fallen victim to,

1:05:43.607 --> 1:05:45.742
quite frankly,
a plantation mentality.

1:05:45.875 --> 1:05:47.811
[Greenberg] I wanna talk
about that mentality.

1:05:47.944 --> 1:05:49.879
That's fucking rich.

1:05:50.014 --> 1:05:52.249
'Cause clearly,
that is at the center
of this entire conversation.

1:05:52.382 --> 1:05:53.984
Your coach, just today,

1:05:54.118 --> 1:05:56.720
