he'd love to be a part of

1:05:56.853 --> 1:05:59.789
and even invoked
the tragic word "slavery."

1:05:59.923 --> 1:06:02.159
I have to ask you,
do you feel

1:06:02.292 --> 1:06:05.662
this is a slave trade
of a different kind?

1:06:05.795 --> 1:06:10.134
-[LeMarcus] Can I give you
another comparison, Greeny?
-Yeah, of course.

1:06:10.267 --> 1:06:13.637
This is the home
of my best friend
and teammate, Emmett Sunday.

1:06:13.770 --> 1:06:16.273
Emmett's father is a farmer
outside Lincoln, Nebraska,

1:06:16.406 --> 1:06:18.242
and his mother
is a teacher's assistant.

1:06:18.375 --> 1:06:20.144
They've saved up
a little bit for retirement,

1:06:20.277 --> 1:06:22.279
but mostly, they just live
month to month.

1:06:22.412 --> 1:06:25.815
One swollen appendix,
one turned ankle
from insolvency.

1:06:25.949 --> 1:06:28.352
Now, their son, Emmett Sunday,
has been a four-year starter

1:06:28.485 --> 1:06:30.654
for one of the best college
programs in the country.

1:06:30.787 --> 1:06:32.389
Tomorrow,
he'll play in a game

1:06:32.522 --> 1:06:34.658
that'll gross over
a half a billion dollars.

1:06:34.791 --> 1:06:36.693
Half a billion dollars
for a single game.

1:06:36.826 --> 1:06:38.228
And Emmett
won't see a dime.

1:06:38.362 --> 1:06:39.829
His football days
will be over.

1:06:39.963 --> 1:06:42.399
Zero compensation,
zero medical insurance

1:06:42.532 --> 1:06:45.102
for the injuries
he's sustained,
some of them permanent.

1:06:45.235 --> 1:06:46.803
And now, this...

1:06:48.172 --> 1:06:49.973
is the Palm Beach
vacation home

1:06:50.107 --> 1:06:52.209
for my coach,
James Lazor.

1:06:53.610 --> 1:06:55.612
This is
his Chicago penthouse.

1:06:57.814 --> 1:07:00.016
This is his
six-bedroom Craftsman,

1:07:00.150 --> 1:07:01.685
where he stays
during the season.

1:07:01.818 --> 1:07:03.220
His work home.

1:07:03.353 --> 1:07:05.522
Now, Coach has profited
off a system

1:07:05.655 --> 1:07:07.857
that is entirely based
on free labor.

1:07:07.991 --> 1:07:10.427
We're not playing in any games
until those who actually play--

1:07:10.560 --> 1:07:13.430
And not just the superstars.
All athletes, down to
the special teams...

1:07:13.563 --> 1:07:16.566
-Jesus.
-...are considered
and compensated.

1:07:16.700 --> 1:07:18.502
[Orlando sighs]
Now.

1:07:18.635 --> 1:07:20.637
This crazy motherfucker.
[chuckles]

1:07:20.770 --> 1:07:23.207
There you have it,
directly from
LeMarcus James.

1:07:23.340 --> 1:07:25.709
LeMarcus,
thank you very much.
All right, LeMarcus.

1:07:25.842 --> 1:07:28.378
[Greenberg]
I appreciate the time.
We'll take a short break,

1:07:28.512 --> 1:07:30.647
and be back with more
in just a moment.

1:07:30.780 --> 1:07:33.083
What the calamitous fuck?

1:07:33.217 --> 1:07:35.619
We've been goddamn
outflanked by two kids,

1:07:35.752 --> 1:07:37.421
like we're
in Scooby fucking Doo.

1:07:37.554 --> 1:07:39.589
Oh, you know what
the dipshit sidekick did

1:07:39.723 --> 1:07:42.058
when LeMarcus
was grandstanding on TV?

1:07:42.192 --> 1:07:43.460
[Katherine] Sunday.
Huh?

1:07:43.593 --> 1:07:45.295
His name is
Emmett Sunday.

1:07:45.429 --> 1:07:47.063
Oh, thank God
we got that all cleared up.

1:07:47.197 --> 1:07:51.501
Emmett fucking-us-sideways
Sunday leaks
my Nike contract.

1:07:51.635 --> 1:07:53.703
Now every New York City
zig-zag's

1:07:53.837 --> 1:07:56.072
asking me where
$30 million a year goes.

1:07:56.206 --> 1:07:57.541
[Katherine]
Where does it go?

1:07:57.674 --> 1:07:59.243
How the hell do I know?

1:07:59.376 --> 1:08:01.345
You're the head
of the conference.

1:08:01.478 --> 1:08:02.679
Excuse me?

1:08:02.812 --> 1:08:04.714
You're the head
of your conference.

1:08:04.848 --> 1:08:07.751
You should be able to answer
a layup like where
your sneaker money goes.

1:08:08.918 --> 1:08:10.654
Okay.

1:08:10.787 --> 1:08:11.955
Band fields.

1:08:12.088 --> 1:08:13.657
Softball stadiums.
[cell phone chimes]

1:08:13.790 --> 1:08:16.926
Turquoise-green
Bermuda fucking sod.
Where else?

